Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.42,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:233758,235426}{\i1}Oww…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.51,Default,Sune,0,0,0,,{TIME:235426,237512}{\i1}But… you did it, Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.12,0:04:27.83,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:266124,267834}Wait, this is my debut song.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.54,0:04:31.25,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:268543,271254}You're right. It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.42,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:271254,272422}Who's singing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:34.38,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:272422,274382}Sounds like Nozomi…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:36.42,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:274382,276426}But there's no way she's that good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:42.93,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:280555,282932}{\i1}The idea to let her play\Nwith the divers was a good call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:46.35,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:282932,286352}{\i1}Nozomi wasn't capable\Nof this volume before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:49.35,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:286352,289355}{\i1}And above all, you can hear\Nthat she puts heart into it.{NOTE:それに何よりも 望みの歌には心がある}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:56.15,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:294569,296154}{\i1}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:31.79,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:267417,271796}{\fad(4000,0)\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  where have you gone?  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:あなたはいない}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:40.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:271796,280180}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  The memory of you  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}  comes back to haunt me  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:あなたの思いでをやさしく}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:48.27,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:280180,288271}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  It slowly decays in my mind  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:胸にしまうの}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.27,0:04:51.77,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:288271,291774}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}  Up in the sky  {\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:青い}
