Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:07.09,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:305538,307090}You're such a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:08.75,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:307090,308750}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:12.33,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:308750,312337}You were singing my debut song\Nto promote yourself to Mr. Egawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:15.67,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:312337,315673}You want to belittle me in his eyes.\NI can't believe how low you've sunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:16.79,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:315673,316799}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:19.92,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:316799,319928}Why did you steal my song, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:21.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:319928,321721}Steal?…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:27.06,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:321721,327060}I knew you were born in a poor house,\Nbut I didn't know you were so rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.06,0:05:28.39,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:327060,328394}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:32.48,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:328394,332482}Why are you giving me that look?\NWhat do you have to defend yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.40,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:333066,334400}I asked her to sing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:38.11,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:336361,338112}Why did you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:39.82,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:338112,339822}I had no particular reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:42.78,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:339822,342784}I just wanted to hear her sing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.78,0:05:46.07,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:342784,346079}By the way, what brings\Nyou here at such hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:49.70,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:347580,349707}We still have a week until recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.66,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:349707,352669}It was decided that we'll hold\Na press conference before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.66,0:05:55.58,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:352669,355588}It'd be an honor if you were\Nto participate in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.71,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:358466,360718}If it was only this,\Nyou could've just called.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:02.51,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:360718,362512}See, Mom? I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:06.76,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:362512,366766}Mr. Egawa didn't hesitate for a moment\Nto accept our invitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:13.06,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:366766,373064}A good teacher is always happy to look after\Nhis student's career beyond their debut.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:15.77,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:373064,375775}I never said I'd agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:17.77,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:375775,377777}My response is no.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.98,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:378319,380989}I am only committed to giving\Nyou singing lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.98,0:06:24.40,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:380989,384409}I don't remember agreeing to do your\Nadvertising or go to your press conferences.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:29.33,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:385159,389330}Furthermore, I no longer want to hear\Nabout moral obligations towards my students.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:31.95,Default,(mixed),0,0,0,,{TIME:389330,391958}– Maestro…\N– Sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:34.16,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:392792,394168}Back to you, Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:394168,395461}Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:39.46,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:396045,399465}Starting tomorrow, you'll sing in\Nthe evening at a night club in Yokohama.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:43.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:401801,403720}A night club in Yokohama?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:403720,405471}Is it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:47.47,Default,Egawa Isao,0,0,0,,{TIME:406431,407473}Here's your score.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:54.68,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:412228,414689}{\i1}"Lady Tady"…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:56.48,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:414689,416482}{\i1}"Lady Tady".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:04.24,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:420528,424240}I'm sorry, do you know which way\Nis the club named "Lady Tady"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:07.49,Default,Random,0,0,0,,{TIME:424240,427493}"Lady Tady"?\NCan't say it rings a bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.07,0:07:10.03,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:428077,430038}Here, it's marked on the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:16.87,Default,Random,0,0,0,,{TIME:431414,436878}Ah, looks like it's in Chinatown,\Nin a side street to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:18.50,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:436878,438504}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.84,0:07:22.46,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:440840,442467}{\i1}There's Chinatown…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.46,0:07:24.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:443468,444927}{\i1}A side street to the left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:29.47,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:447513,449474}{\i1}I think this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.73,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:454062,455730}Maybe I heard him wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:37.52,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:455730,457523}That's not it…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:38.98,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:457523,458983}Not there either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:41.44,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:459942,461444}Looks like this is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.62,Default,Bouncer,0,0,0,,{TIME:473206,474624}Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:59.37,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:474624,479379}I'm Mine Nozomi.\NMr. Egawa has sent me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.37,0:08:00.33,Default,Bouncer,0,0,0,,{TIME:479379,480338}This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.05,Default,Club owner,0,0,0,,{TIME:482965,485051}So you're Mine Nozomi-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:07.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:485051,487887}Yes. Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.38,Default,Club owner,0,0,0,,{TIME:487887,489389}Have a sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:10.84,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:489389,490848}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.47,0:08:13.81,Default,Club owner,0,0,0,,{TIME:492475,493810}So young…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.06,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:493810,495061}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:19.85,Default,Club owner,0,0,0,,{TIME:495061,499857}Oh, nothing. A member of the band will\Nbe here soon. Could you wait for him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:21.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:499857,501025}Naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:506614,508282}Nitta-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.28,0:08:29.65,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:508282,509659}Nozomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:34.91,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:510410,514914}I heard we'll have a new singer.\NSo it was you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.12,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:514914,516124}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.12,0:08:40.04,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:516124,520044}But frankly I feel bad seeing a cute girl\Nlike you in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:42.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:520044,522088}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:45.09,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:523297,525091}You'll see for yourself soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:49.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:525967,529929}But I'm so glad that I get to sing\Naccompanied by your trumpet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:529929,531597}I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:58.52,Default,Bouncer,0,0,0,,{TIME:536227,538521}Nicchan, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.53,0:09:09.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:548531,549907}My name is Mine Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:14.12,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:549907,554120}I'm the new singer here and I'll do my best.\NI hope you'll like my songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:37.60,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:569760,577602}{\i1}Nozomi meets Nitta Akira again, a trumpeter\Nshe first met during her Tōhoku tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:44.06,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:577602,584066}{\i1}The ability to sing to her old friend's trumpet\Nmakes Nozomi feel joy and a bit of nostalgia.
Comment: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:50.86,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:574307,590865}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:あなたにX私\\N本当に嘘じゃないのね}
Comment: 0,0:09:50.86,0:09:58.58,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:590865,598581}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:こんなに女の人は}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.59,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:609509,612595}Keep singing.\NThey want to intimidate you.{NOTE:だから 君だけに投稿できているんだけど}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.34,0:10:16.05,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:613346,616057}You can't lose to them.\NContinue, Nozomi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.05,0:10:17.26,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:616057,617266}Keep singing.
Comment: 0,0:10:17.68,0:10:25.90,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:617683,625900}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:今ならXX}
Comment: 0,0:10:25.90,0:10:34.28,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:625900,634283}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:あなたをXX}
Comment: 0,0:10:34.28,0:10:42.45,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:634283,642458}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}{NOTE:このままXXたら}
Comment: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:48.17,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:642458,648172}{\an8\fnArial}♪{\fn}\N{\fnArial}♪{\fn}
Comment: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:51.17,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:648965,651175}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.80,0:10:53.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:651801,653010}Nitta-san…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.09,Default,Billy Jones,0,0,0,,{TIME:655680,657098}Outta my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.97,0:11:00.10,Default,Billy Jones,0,0,0,,{TIME:658975,660101}Get away from that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.89,Default,Billy Jones,0,0,0,,{TIME:662853,664897}Come back when you learn\Nto play the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:06.94,Default,Pianist,0,0,0,,{TIME:665982,666941}What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.90,0:11:09.69,Default,Pianist,0,0,0,,{TIME:667900,669694}How about you play it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:26.04,Default,Pianist,0,0,0,,{TIME:684166,686043}Ha. That's all you can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.37,0:11:30.13,Default,Audience,0,0,0,,{TIME:688379,690131}Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:33.75,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:690840,693759}{\i1}Something's changed in his eyes\Nas he was about to press a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:36.09,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:693759,696095}{\i1}What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:39.59,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:696095,699599}{\i1}Anyway, that's a nice mess\NI've gotten myself into, indeed.
Comment: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:47.29,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:707290,707290}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:53.42,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:710835,713421}Time for a break.\NLet's get some ramen. It's my treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:54.79,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:713421,714797}For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:56.38,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:714797,716382}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:59.38,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:717717,719385}Do you know who\Nthat foreigner was?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.38,0:12:00.72,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:719385,720720}Nope, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:01.76,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:720720,721762}He's Bill Jones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:02.80,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:721762,722805}Bill Jones?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:06.85,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:722805,726851}He was once a famous Dixieland pianist\Nin New Orleans. He was an absolute legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:13.94,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:731981,733941}How did he end up like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:17.52,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:733941,737528}I heard he had lost his lover\Nwhile he was on a concert tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.52,0:12:20.74,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:737528,740740}He was given the news while on stage.\NHe's been unable to play ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.74,0:12:23.24,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:740740,743242}He drifted for a long, long time\Nbefore arriving to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:25.82,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:743242,745828}Now no one remembers him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:28.49,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:745828,748497}I learned he was the Bill Jones\Nonly by accident, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.49,0:12:33.75,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:748497,753753}One night, when he was dead drunk, I had\Nto drive him home. That's how I met him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:38.79,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:753753,758799}At first, I just couldn't\Nbelieve he was the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.79,0:12:40.50,Default,Ramen,0,0,0,,{TIME:758799,760509}Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:44.51,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:763137,764513}Surprising, huh? That club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:46.01,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:765181,766015}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.64,0:12:51.10,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:768642,771103}This audience has the most fun\Nwhen it teases the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.10,0:12:53.60,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:771103,773606}We had many singers like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:56.56,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:773606,776567}But eventually none of them\Nlasted more than a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.65,0:13:00.90,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:777651,780905}Now, don't get it wrong.\NThe guests' sense of music is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:04.49,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:780905,784492}Take for example the guy who played\Nthe piano. He's actually pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.49,0:13:09.12,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:784492,789121}Bill Jones stopped him because\Nhe thought he was not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:12.16,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:789789,792166}In any case, I had never\Nseen such thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:15.08,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:792166,795086}This is why, even if they whistle\Nat me, I don't mean to give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:17.04,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:795086,797046}It's a good learning experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:18.13,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:797046,798130}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.67,0:13:26.18,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:802676,806180}You have to be really very good\Nto please that kind of audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:29.64,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:806180,809642}After all, don't forget that they are\Nthe ones who created the jazz.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:34.64,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:810393,814647}If they whistle at me, there can be only one\Nexplanation: that I'm not good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:43.65,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:819318,823656}But I am sure that one day I will be able to\Nmake them respect and listen to me in quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:48.32,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:825241,828327}Until that day comes,\NI won't give up, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:49.91,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:828327,829912}That's what I had decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.12,0:13:54.08,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:831122,834083}Nitta-san.\NI'm not going to leave, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.08,0:13:57.87,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:834083,837878}But I'm afraid you can't do much with the songs\Nyou sing. They're all Japanese love ballads.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.87,0:14:01.13,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:837878,841132}No matter how hard you try,\Nyou won't change your style overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:05.88,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:841132,845886}I agree, but I've been\Nsent here by Mr. Egawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:11.64,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:845886,851642}They come here to listen to jazz.\NAnything else will get whistled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:15.02,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:852726,855020}At any rate, I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:19.90,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:855729,859900}{\i1}Nozomi felt encouraged\Nafter talking to Nitta.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:23.90,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:859900,863904}{\i1}Day after day, she continued to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:28.90,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:863904,868909}{\i1}But the audience still\Nrefused to listen to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:41.83,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:876208,881839}{\i1}Days passed by as exhausted Nozomi\Nwas going home by the last train.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.83,0:14:43.92,Default,Conductor,0,0,0,,{TIME:881839,883924}Excuse me, it's the end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:44.93,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:883924,884934}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.93,0:14:46.55,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:884934,886552}Ah! I overslept!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:48.92,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:886552,888929}I missed my stop again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:57.43,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:894685,897438}What do you say?\NShe's not bad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:15:00.44,Default,Nohara Jun,0,0,0,,{TIME:898063,900441}I'd never tell she's still\Nbasically an amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.40,0:15:10.99,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:909408,910993}Good morning, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:14.37,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:910993,914371}We will hold the press conference\Nin the room we reserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.37,0:15:16.12,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:914371,916123}I'm sorry, but please\Nwait for a few more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.12,0:15:18.12,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:916123,918125}Oh, where's Mr. Egawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.83,0:15:21.46,Default,Kōda Sumiyo,0,0,0,,{TIME:918834,921462}Oh? He was here just moments ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.75,0:15:26.25,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:922755,926258}Nozomi-san, look for\NMr. Egawa and call him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.25,0:15:28.80,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:926258,928802}Oh, if you're looking for him,\Nhe's just gone home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:30.80,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:928802,930804}Then hurry up and bring him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.01,0:15:34.18,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:932014,934183}I'm not sure if it's such a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.18,0:15:36.47,Default,Kōda Miki,0,0,0,,{TIME:934183,936477}What did you say?! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.14,0:15:41.48,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:937144,941482}Well, he did say earlier that he didn't\Nwant to go to your press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:43.23,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:941857,943234}Besides, he's busy today.
