Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.77,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027651,1029778}{\i1}Nozomi trembled with anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.77,0:17:17.78,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1030779,1037786}{\i1}However, as she continued to sing in vain\Nwith words that no one could understand,
