Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.14,0:17:45.35,Default,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1060142,1065356}{\i1}As time went by, Nozomi was\Ngetting more anxious and nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:05.66,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081830,1085668}{\i1}How long do I have to wait before\NI can become a real singer?
