Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.31,0:18:29.23,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106313,1109233}{\i1}I didn't forget my song.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.90,0:18:33.94,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1109900,1113946}{\i1}I can still sing.\NI can sing more than enough!
