Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.49,0:18:41.24,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119493,1121245}{\i1}Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.37,0:18:48.25,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1126375,1128252}I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:53.63,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1128961,1133632}If nobody listens to me\Neither way, I'll sing for you, Fanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:55.25,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133632,1135259}For you only.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:22.36,Default,Pianist,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160492,1162369}What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.36,0:19:24.53,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162369,1164538}Stop it! Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.53,0:19:26.03,Default,Nitta Akira,0,0,0,,{TIME:1164538,1166039}Hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.54,0:19:32.17,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1169543,1172171}{\i1}I have to sing.\NNo matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:35.25,Default,Mine Nozomi,0,0,0,,{TIME:1172171,1175257}{\i1}Nobody is listening to me.\NIt's the perfect moment.
